text: Dinastía (born July 20, 1994) is the ring name of a Mexican Luchador enmascarado who works in the Mini-Estrella division for Lucha Libre AAA Worldwide where he is the current AAA World Mini-Estrella Champion in his second reign. His real name is not a matter of public record, as is often the case with masked wrestlers in Mexico, where their private lives are kept a secret from the wrestling fans.
